 beyond its religious roots, Easter has woven itself into the fabric of societies globally, symbolising themes of renewal, hope, and joy. This blog explores the multifaceted importance of Easter and highlights organisations that play a pivotal role in promoting its values worldwide.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1493_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1494_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1495_">The essence of Easter</h3><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1497_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">At its heart, Easter commemorates the resurrection of Jesus Christ, an event that lies at the very core of the Christian faith. This celebration of life over death offers believers a profound message of hope, affirming the possibility of new beginnings and the promise of eternal life. Yet, the influence of Easter extends far beyond church walls, permeating various aspects of culture, society, and even the economy.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1499_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/happy-african-american-siblings-and-grandparents-i-2023-11-27-04-55-40-utc.jpg?v=1709634777" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/happy-african-american-siblings-and-grandparents-i-2023-11-27-04-55-40-utc.jpg?v=1709634777 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Easter 2024 Celebrations: A Comprehensive Guide to Joyful Festivities - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Easter 2024 Celebrations: A Comprehensive Guide to Joyful Festivities - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1500_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1501_" tabindex="0" spe