y Training Group UK -" title="Unveiling Easter Traditions and Customs: A Global Perspective - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1590_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1591_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Wavebreakmedia via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1593_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Easter traditions vary widely across the globe, each adding its unique hue to the celebration's rich cultural tapestry. From the solemnity of Holy Week processions in Spain to the vibrant Easter egg hunts in the United States, these customs reflect a harmonious blend of Christian and pre-Christian symbols, such as eggs and rabbits, which embody fertility and renewal.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1595_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1596_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1597_">Unity and community</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-kids-looking-for-eggs-in-a-bag-for-easter-2023-11-27-05-00-56-utc.jpg?v=1709634940" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-kids-looking-for-eggs-in-a-bag-for-easter-2023-11-27-05-00-56-utc.jpg?v=1709634940 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-kids-looking-for-eggs-in-a-bag-for-easter-2023-11-27-05-00-56-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709634940 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-kids-looking-for-eggs-in-a-bag-for-easter-2023-11-27-05-00-56-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709634940 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Fostering Easter Community Engagement: How to Get Involved - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Fostering Easter Community Engagement: How to Get Involved - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Trai