cultural and religious boundaries, offering everyone a moment to contemplate personal growth and renewal.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1622_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1623_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1624_">Supporting and celebrating Easter</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/bunny-boy-and-his-family-2023-11-27-05-07-43-utc.jpg?v=1709635155" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/bunny-boy-and-his-family-2023-11-27-05-07-43-utc.jpg?v=1709635155 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/bunny-boy-and-his-family-2023-11-27-05-07-43-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709635155 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/bunny-boy-and-his-family-2023-11-27-05-07-43-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709635155 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Exploring the Cultural Significance of Easter Around the World - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Exploring the Cultural Significance of Easter Around the World - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1626_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1627_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Pressmaster via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1629_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Various organisations, both within the UK and globally, play a crucial role in raising awareness about the significance of Easter and supporting its celebrations:</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-1631_"><li tabindex="0" spell